                    <li><p><a href="https://www.bfi.org.uk/events-adult-learners" class="">Join events and activities for families</a></p></li>
                    <li><p><a href="https://www.bfi.org.uk/bfi-reuben-library" class="">BFI Reuben Library</a></p></li>
                  </ul>
        </div>
                <div class="close-button"></div>
      </li>
      <li class="nav-highlight">
              </li>
      <li class="nav-actions">
                <p class="h4">I want to&hellip;</p>
        <ul>
                      <li><p><a href="https://www.bfi.org.uk/bfi-national-archive/research-bfi-archive" class="">Search the BFI National Archive collections</a></p></li>
                      <li><p><a href="https://whatson.bfi.org.uk/Online/default.asp?BOparam::WScontent::loadArticle::permalink=education-events" class="">Browse our education events</a></p></li>
                      <li><p><a href="https://www.bfi.org.uk/education-research/teaching-film-tv-media-studies" class="">Use film and TV in my classroom</a></p></li>
                      <li><p><a href="https://www.bfi.org.uk/industry-data-insights" class="">Read research data and market intelligence</a></p></li>
                  </ul>
              </li>
    </ul>
      </li>
          <li class="desktop" id="top_nav_3">
    <p><a href="https://www.bfi.org.uk/funding-industry"  data-drop-content="drop-nav-3" class="medium expand button">Funding and industry</a>
      <span class="arrow"></span>    </p>
        <ul class="small-block-grid-3 drop-content" id="drop-nav-3">
      <li class="nav-sublist">
                <div class="box primary">
        <p class="h4">In this section</p>
