<div class="block">
      
  <div class="content">
    <div class="full-title with-title-branding">
      <div class="title-branding"><a href="/taxonomy/term/868"><img src="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/sites/bfi.org.uk/files/styles/16x9_small/public/sight-and-sound-logo-280x69.png?itok=AEegRSbk" alt="" /></a></div>
  
  <h1>
          At home (and away) with Agnès Varda    
    
      </h1>

  
  
        <div class="copy">
              <div class="intro"><p>Free-spirited grande dame of the cinema and now gallery, Agnès Varda can’t stop moving, gleaning, probing. “We are millions,” she tells Daniel Trilling, welcoming him into her living home of cinema.</p>
</div>
            
      
              <p class="author-data">
          <span class="author"> Daniel  Trilling  </span><br /><span class="date">Updated: <time datetime="2019-03-29">29 March 2019</time></span>        </p>
      
      
          </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="block">
      
  <div class="content">
    
  <ul class="share">
          <li class="facebook_share"><div class="fb-share-button" data-href="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/interviews/home-away-agn-s-varda" data-layout="button_count"></div>
</li>
          <li class="field_tweetbutton"><div class="tweetbutton-tweet tweetbutton"><a href="http://twitter.com/share" data-size="medium" data-count="horizontal" data-via="SightSoundmag" data-related=":" data-text="At home (and away) with Agnès..." data-counturl="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/interviews/home-away-agn-s-varda" data-url="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/interviews/home-away-agn-s-varda" data-lang="" class="twitter-share-button">Tweet</a></div></li>
          <li class="pinterest"><a href="//pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/interviews/home-away-agn-s-varda&description=At home (and away) with Agnès Varda&media=https://www2.bfi.org.uk/sites/bfi.org.uk/files/news/varda-agnes-001-portrait-1000x750.jpg" data-pin-do="buttonPin" data-pin-config="beside" data-pin-zero="true"><img src="//assets.pinterest.com/images/pidgets/pin_it_button.png" /></a></li>
      </ul>

  <div class='social_sidebar'>
  	<ul>
	            <li class="facebook_share"><div class="fb-share-button" data-href="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/interviews/home-away-agn-s-varda" data-layout="box_count"></div>
</li>
		          <li class="field_tweetbutton"><div class="tweetbutton-tweet tweetbutton"><a href="http://twitter.com/share" data-size="medium" data-count="vertical" data-via="SightSoundmag" data-related=":" data-text="At home (and away) with Agnès..." data-counturl="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/interviews/home-away-agn-s-varda" data-url="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/interviews/home-away-agn-s-varda" data-lang="" class="twitter-share-button">Tweet</a></div></li>
